relation: Darrow3 - #81 Having arrived at Winters, Jeff reunites with his father at long last. Of course, knowing Dr. Andonuts' track record of following his son's life, the result is...less than joyous.

Darrow3 - #80 With the next goal in mind, the party leaves Eagleland bound for Winters so they can modify the Sky Runner for the next leg of the journey. Perhaps they may even find more than they expected during this little side trip.

Darrow - #38 Remembering Picky's motto, Ness suddenly awakens to a new possiblity. Remember, when a young main hero is at the end of his ropes, a special skill will always save him at the last minute!
Darrow3 - #79 Returning to Threed once more, Jeff finally reunites with the Sky Runner...which has been the victim of an unexpected accident.

Darrow3 - #78 Stepping outside, Ness encounters Picky, who has become a victim of a broken family after the recent events. With his father and brother having ditched home for their own selfish desires, all that's left is him and Lardna. A home that, surely, is more than frightening than zombie Threed any day of the week.
